110
00:07:42.503 --> 00:07:43.963  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Check your sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:44.046 --> 00:07:46.299  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
