113
00:07:51.387 --> 00:07:52.722  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take him to the brig.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:04.817 --> 00:08:06.235  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Halt turbolift.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:07.487 --> 00:08:09.071  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engineering.</c.bg_transparent>

116
