<c.bg_transparent>Just don't do anything you'll regret.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:32.446 --> 00:09:33.823  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Move.</c.bg_transparent>

137
