00:11:23.849 --> 00:11:25.226  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>l think so. Why?</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:25.518 --> 00:11:26.977  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
