170
00:11:27.061 --> 00:11:28.145  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What for?</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:28.562 --> 00:11:30.606  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf I'm going to put the ship</c.bg_transparent>
