<c.bg_transparent>l need help.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:39.031 --> 00:11:40.074  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:41.784 --> 00:11:42.910  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where are my officers?</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:43.577 --> 00:11:45.704  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
