<c.bg_transparent>at least partly.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:51.377 --> 00:11:53.212  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean about your being</c.bg_transparent>
