<c.bg_transparent>from a pound on Taris Seti IV.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:14.275 --> 00:12:18.362  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She was the runt of the litter,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you thought she had spunk.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:12:18.446 --> 00:12:21.031  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You love music, but you never learned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to play an instrument--</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:21.490 --> 00:12:23.117  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
