<c.bg_transparent>My ready room.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:49.018  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a fascinating story,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but as the Ferengi say,</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:49.310 --> 00:12:52.062  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>''A good lie is easier to believe</c.bg_transparent>
