195
00:12:52.146 --> 00:12:53.731  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, you're saying no one on your crew</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:53.814 --> 00:12:56.358  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>has encountered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one of these temporal barriers?</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:57.151 --> 00:13:00.321  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My helmsman disappeared</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when she tried to walk down that corridor,</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:00.404 --> 00:13:03.782  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but that doesn't prove she passed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through a temporal barrier.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:04.116 --> 00:13:07.203  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf you inject yourself,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>l can take you down that corridor</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:07.286 --> 00:13:10.039  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and show you everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I've said is true.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:11.165 --> 00:13:14.210  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have Mr. Kim run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a full-spectral analysis.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:13:14.293 --> 00:13:15.961  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
