305
00:18:48.710 --> 00:18:51.046  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we project a chroniton field</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>throughout the vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:51.130 --> 00:18:52.131  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How?</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:53.215 --> 00:18:56.135  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Each cube has</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>specially designed conduits.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:18:56.510 --> 00:18:59.429  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf we install similar conduits</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>throughout this vessel</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:18:59.513 --> 00:19:01.473  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then generate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a sufficiently powerful field,</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:01.557 --> 00:19:04.393  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we may be able to force </c.bg_transparent><i><c.bg_transparent>Voyager</c.bg_transparent></i>
<c.bg_transparent>back into temporal sync.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:19:04.476 --> 00:19:06.395  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Temporal sync with what?</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:19:07.688 --> 00:19:11.692  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The vessel will return to the moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the original chronokinetic surge.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:19:12.109 --> 00:19:14.528  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Since the surge will last</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for six to seven seconds,</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:19:14.611 --> 00:19:16.446  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Chakotay</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will have a short time</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:16.530 --> 00:19:19.741  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in which to try to counteract</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the warp core reaction.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:19:19.825 --> 00:19:22.494  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if we could replicate these conduits,</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:19:22.578 --> 00:19:24.663  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we'd have no way to get them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through the temporal barriers.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:19:26.039 --> 00:19:27.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The bio-neural circuitry.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:28.292 --> 00:19:29.668  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:19:29.751 --> 00:19:32.462  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It runs through every section of the ship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>almost like a nervous system.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:19:33.338 --> 00:19:36.216  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf we could inject the gel packs</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with your serum,</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:36.383 --> 00:19:39.386  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we could use them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to transmit the chroniton field.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:39.553 --> 00:19:42.639  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The warp core could be recalibrated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to generate that field.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:43.182 --> 00:19:44.433  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Work on it.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:44.600 --> 00:19:46.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chakotay and l will see</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about modifying the serum.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:46.727 --> 00:19:48.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your plan is inefficient.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:49.229 --> 00:19:50.230  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:50.397 --> 00:19:51.773  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are only two of you.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:51.940 --> 00:19:54.276  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf l were to assimilate you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into a small Borg collective,</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:54.443 --> 00:19:55.944  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you could then assimilate others.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:56.111 --> 00:19:58.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The work would proceed more quickly.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:58.447 --> 00:20:00.949  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry, but l like my plan better.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:01.116 --> 00:20:02.743  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be back.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:20:10.334 --> 00:20:12.711  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was an interesting experience.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:20:12.878 --> 00:20:14.129  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf it makes you feel any better,</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:20:14.296 --> 00:20:16.423  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're going to develop quite a knack</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for dealing with the Borg.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:20:16.590 --> 00:20:18.717  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean we're going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be seeing more of them?</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:20:18.884 --> 00:20:21.261  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll run into them on a few occasions.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:20:21.428 --> 00:20:24.306  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do l get the feeling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's an understatement?</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:20:25.349 --> 00:20:29.436  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't seem like my first command</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is shaping up the way l expected.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:20:29.603 --> 00:20:32.606  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the middle of the journey of our life,</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:20:32.773 --> 00:20:35.734  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>l found myself astray in a dark wood</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:20:35.901 --> 00:20:39.112  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>where the straight road had been lost.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:20:40.072 --> 00:20:43.325  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>l didn't know Dante's </c.bg_transparent><i><c.bg_transparent>Inferno</c.bg_transparent></i>
<c.bg_transparent>was on the Maquis reading list.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:20:44.076 --> 00:20:46.245  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, l borrowed your copy.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:20:47.621 --> 00:20:49.831  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My fiancé gave me that book</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as an engagement gift.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:20:49.998 --> 00:20:51.667  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never lent it to anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:20:51.833 --> 00:20:53.126  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not yet.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:20:54.544 --> 00:20:56.588  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anyway, l agree with Dante.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:20:56.755 --> 00:20:58.799  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lf you always see</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the road ahead of you,</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:20:58.966 --> 00:21:00.509  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it's not worth the trip.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:21:01.009 --> 00:21:03.679  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A soldier and a philosopher.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:21:04.721 --> 00:21:07.724  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your intelligence file</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't do you justice.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:21:08.976 --> 00:21:11.144  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've replicated these belts</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to resist the effects</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:21:11.311 --> 00:21:14.398  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of the temporal barriers,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just like the hyposprays.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:21:14.564 --> 00:21:17.150  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>l didn't realize you were programmed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be so versatile.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:21:17.317 --> 00:21:20.362  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>l wasn't, but when you are thrown</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into the deep end of the galaxy</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:21:20.529 --> 00:21:22.739  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and left running</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for as long as I've been,</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:21:22.906 --> 00:21:25.575  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it helps to develop</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a few extra subroutines.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:21:25.742 --> 00:21:27.411  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long have you been running?</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:21:27.577 --> 00:21:30.998  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Almost three years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since our original doctor was killed.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:21:31.164 --> 00:21:33.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Killed? How?</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:21:33.166 --> 00:21:35.335  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the incident that stranded us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>here in the Delta Qua--</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:21:35.502 --> 00:21:36.712  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:21:39.464 --> 00:21:42.092  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Temporal Prime Directive, remember?</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:21:42.342 --> 00:21:43.802  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:21:44.553 --> 00:21:46.138  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:21:47.681 --> 00:21:51.018  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Delta Quadrant?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Is that what he was about to say?</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:21:51.810 --> 00:21:52.978  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:21:55.355 --> 00:21:57.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take the upper decks,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you take the lower.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:21:57.733 --> 00:21:59.526  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>l don't think splitting up's a good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:21:59.693 --> 00:22:01.153  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll get the job done faster.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:22:01.320 --> 00:22:03.739  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As your first officer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's my duty to protect you.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:22:03.905 --> 00:22:06.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>l know a lot more about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what's out there than you do,</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:22:06.199 --> 00:22:08.702  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and we have no way of communicating</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if something goes wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:22:08.869 --> 00:22:10.871  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It may take a little longer,</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:22:11.079 --> 00:22:12.956  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we should go together.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:22:14.124 --> 00:22:15.667  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>After you...</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:22:16.209 --> 00:22:17.753  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:22:33.101 --> 00:22:34.519  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I ask you something?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:22:35.812 --> 00:22:38.148  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I started off with a crew of 153.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:22:39.024 --> 00:22:41.151  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I already know I lost my doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:22:41.985 --> 00:22:43.445  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many others?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:22:44.571 --> 00:22:46.823  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll suffer casualties</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like any other starship,</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:22:47.741 --> 00:22:49.659  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you'll also gain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>new crewmen as well.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:22:50.118 --> 00:22:51.119  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like you.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:22:51.870 --> 00:22:54.122  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you get to be my first officer?</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:22:55.082 --> 00:22:58.210  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our crews will be forced to work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>together after we get stranded.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:22:58.502 --> 00:23:00.087  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the Delta Quadrant?</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:23:01.379 --> 00:23:02.881  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How does that happen?</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:23:04.424 --> 00:23:06.093  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure you want to know?</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:23:12.140 --> 00:23:13.225  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[loud buzzing]</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:23:15.143 --> 00:23:16.186  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Run!</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:23:22.150 --> 00:23:23.652  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What the hell was that?</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:23:24.528 --> 00:23:27.614  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A macro virus. They infected the ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a few years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:23:29.241 --> 00:23:32.828  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds like it's going to be one</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>disaster after another on this ship.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:23:33.578 --> 00:23:35.372  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You once told me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Starfleet captains</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:23:35.539 --> 00:23:38.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>don't choose their missions,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the missions choose them.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:23:38.542 --> 00:23:40.418  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going to have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the opportunity to study things</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:23:40.585 --> 00:23:42.337  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no human has ever seen before.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:23:42.879 --> 00:23:45.090  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Including some very large germs.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:23:55.100 --> 00:23:57.310  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A monochromatic environment?</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:23:57.602 --> 00:23:59.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's called "black and white."</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:23:59.771 --> 00:24:02.065  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's one of Tom Paris'</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>holodeck programs.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:24:02.941 --> 00:24:05.986  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He based it on some old</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>science fiction serials.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:24:06.403 --> 00:24:08.238  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interesting technology.</c.bg_transparent>

407
