<c.bg_transparent>and medical supplies,</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:30:31.496 --> 00:30:33.289  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or we're going to have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a lot more casualties.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:30:33.456 --> 00:30:34.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid that isn't possible right now.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:30:35.083 --> 00:30:36.334  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do the best you can.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:30:36.793 --> 00:30:38.419  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sighs]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:30:40.088 --> 00:30:42.048  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's an access panel in the galley.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:30:54.310 --> 00:30:55.770  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Coffee, black.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:30:56.312 --> 00:30:58.147  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how I like my coffee?</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:30:58.731 --> 00:31:01.317  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you haven't changed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your standing order in seven years.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:31:03.152 --> 00:31:05.196  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks. It's just what I needed.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:31:05.905 --> 00:31:08.741  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You'll get us out of this.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:31:08.908 --> 00:31:10.076  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You always do.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:31:11.452 --> 00:31:12.787  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All done here.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:31:12.954 --> 00:31:14.205  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Tuvok]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:31:15.039 --> 00:31:16.416  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tuvok?</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:31:23.047 --> 00:31:25.216  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am pleased you are here.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:31:26.593 --> 00:31:28.761  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I would see you again.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:31:29.429 --> 00:31:30.805  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[gasping]</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:31:31.639 --> 00:31:33.141  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to know,</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:31:34.100 --> 00:31:37.687  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it has been an honor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to serve with you...</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:31:38.271 --> 00:31:40.273  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to be your friend.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:31:44.277 --> 00:31:45.528  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Paris!</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:31:55.330 --> 00:31:58.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Live long and prosper.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:32:04.172 --> 00:32:06.049  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[tricorder beeping]</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:32:07.175 --> 00:32:08.551  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[steady tone sounds]</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:32:29.781 --> 00:32:30.990  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deck 11.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:32:32.241 --> 00:32:34.535  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't let this happen, not again.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:32:35.078 --> 00:32:36.245  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:32:36.454 --> 00:32:38.122  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i><c.bg_transparent>Voyager</c.bg_transparent></i><c.bg_transparent> getting stranded,</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:32:38.289 --> 00:32:41.125  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>all these deaths this entire future,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's my fault.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:32:41.292 --> 00:32:42.794  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to do something to change it.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:32:42.961 --> 00:32:44.253  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you have in mind?</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:32:44.420 --> 00:32:47.465  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we can find a way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to modify Seven of Nine's plan.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:32:47.924 --> 00:32:50.218  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put</c.bg_transparent><i><c.bg_transparent> Voyager</c.bg_transparent></i><c.bg_transparent> into temporal sync</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with my time frame.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:32:50.301 --> 00:32:52.220  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Captain...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Now that I know what's going to happen,</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:32:52.303 --> 00:32:54.973  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could avoid getting trapped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Delta Quadrant in the first place.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:32:55.139 --> 00:32:56.307  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Halt turbolift.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:32:57.100 --> 00:32:59.936  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seven's plan is dangerous enough.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Trying to alter it is too risky.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:33:00.103 --> 00:33:01.396  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's worth the risk.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:33:01.562 --> 00:33:02.730  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If Seven's idea works,</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:33:02.897 --> 00:33:04.691  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tuvok and those other crewmen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:33:04.857 --> 00:33:07.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They'll still be stuck</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Delta Quadrant.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:33:07.527 --> 00:33:10.029  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If a temporal anomaly doesn't kill them,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something else will--</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:33:10.196 --> 00:33:13.074  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Borg, telepathic pitcher plants,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>macroviruses.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:33:13.282 --> 00:33:14.951  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Delta Quadrant is a death trap.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:33:15.118 --> 00:33:17.078  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about the Temporal Prime Directive?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:33:17.161 --> 00:33:18.204  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To hell with it.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:33:19.789 --> 00:33:22.917  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With all due respect,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's a little presumptuous to think</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:33:23.084 --> 00:33:25.294  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you have the right</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to change everyone's future.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:33:25.461 --> 00:33:27.046  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From what I've seen, they'll thank me.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:33:27.338 --> 00:33:29.090  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All you've seen are bits and pieces.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:33:29.257 --> 00:33:31.676  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You're not getting the whole picture.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Really?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:33:31.843 --> 00:33:33.094  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just what am I missing?</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:33:33.636 --> 00:33:35.430  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not what, it's who.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:33:36.139 --> 00:33:37.682  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>People like Seven of Nine,</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:33:38.266 --> 00:33:41.269  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>a Borg drone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who'll become a member of this crew</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:33:41.436 --> 00:33:43.479  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>after you help her</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>recover her humanity.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:33:44.147 --> 00:33:46.024  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or Tom Paris, a former convict</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:33:46.190 --> 00:33:50.528  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>who'll be our pilot, chief medic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a husband to B'Elanna Torres.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:33:50.695 --> 00:33:52.363  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That angry woman I just met?</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:33:52.530 --> 00:33:54.615  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's going to be your chief engineer.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:33:55.033 --> 00:33:58.369  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two crews, Maquis and Starfleet,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are going to become one,</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:33:58.786 --> 00:34:00.872  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they'll make as big a mark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Delta Quadrant</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:34:01.039 --> 00:34:02.540  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as it'll make on them,</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:34:02.707 --> 00:34:04.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>by protecting people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like the Ocampans,</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:34:04.542 --> 00:34:06.544  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>curing diseases, encouraging peace.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:34:07.003 --> 00:34:08.463  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Children like Naomi and Icheb</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:34:08.629 --> 00:34:11.090  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>are going to grow up on</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this ship and call it home.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:34:11.257 --> 00:34:13.968  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And we'll all be following a captain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who sets a course for Earth</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:34:14.135 --> 00:34:16.304  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and never stops believing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that we'll get there.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:34:18.514 --> 00:34:20.224  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you going to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lecturing me like this</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:34:20.391 --> 00:34:21.893  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for the next seven years?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:34:22.393 --> 00:34:25.188  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll always get the last word.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:34:25.897 --> 00:34:27.815  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In that case,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>let's get back to work.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:34:31.235 --> 00:34:32.737  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, who is this Seska?</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:34:33.362 --> 00:34:36.699  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She was a member of my crew</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who turned out to be a Cardassian spy.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:34:36.866 --> 00:34:39.619  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She made an alliance with the Kazon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and took over the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:34:39.827 --> 00:34:41.662  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right. We got it back.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:34:41.913 --> 00:34:44.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sounds like she's not going to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as cooperative as the others.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:34:45.083 --> 00:34:47.710  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest we take a page</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of your rule book.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:34:47.877 --> 00:34:49.253  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We try diplomacy.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:34:49.420 --> 00:34:51.839  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine, but the next page</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that book says</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:34:52.006 --> 00:34:55.093  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that when diplomacy fails,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we need a backup plan.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:34:55.259 --> 00:34:57.303  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Something tells me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you already have one.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:34:58.179 --> 00:35:00.765  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've already injected the gel packs</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the other time frames.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:35:00.932 --> 00:35:02.558  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That just leaves the ones here.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:35:03.309 --> 00:35:05.895  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's in both our interests</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to work together.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:35:08.147 --> 00:35:09.357  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I agree.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:35:09.899 --> 00:35:11.192  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let him go.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:35:11.567 --> 00:35:12.860  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You believe him?</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:35:13.319 --> 00:35:15.822  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His story is too preposterous</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be a lie.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:35:24.997 --> 00:35:27.708  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll admit, it's an ingenious solution.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:35:28.709 --> 00:35:30.294  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad you're cooperating.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:35:31.045 --> 00:35:34.298  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I believe in cooperation,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as long as it benefits me.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:35:36.134 --> 00:35:39.637  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, it's true what they say...</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:35:41.806 --> 00:35:43.432  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:35:43.599 --> 00:35:46.394  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Men just get more distinguished</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as they get older.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:35:46.602 --> 00:35:49.605  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few lines here, a little gray there.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:35:50.606 --> 00:35:51.941  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It adds character.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:35:53.526 --> 00:35:55.695  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Too bad their minds start to go.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:35:56.445 --> 00:35:59.365  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last time you were here,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you had that nasty head injury</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:35:59.532 --> 00:36:03.077  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you mumbled something about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my taking over the ship five years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:36:03.244 --> 00:36:05.329  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If that's true, then you're from</c.bg_transparent>
