615
00:36:05.496 --> 00:36:06.914  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>which means that, at some point,</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:36:07.081 --> 00:36:09.417  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
