<c.bg_transparent>to regain control of </c.bg_transparent><i><c.bg_transparent>Voyager.</c.bg_transparent></i>

617
00:36:09.584 --> 00:36:10.793  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't allow that to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:36:12.170 --> 00:36:14.172  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Step away from the console.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:36:18.092 --> 00:36:19.719  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An ingenious plan.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:36:19.886 --> 00:36:21.846  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It just needs a slight modification.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:36:22.013 --> 00:36:23.389  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:36:23.723 --> 00:36:24.765  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recalibrating your pulse</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:36:24.932 --> 00:36:27.476  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bring the ship into temporal sync</c.bg_transparent>
