625
00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:31.772  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When will you learn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to stop underestimating me?</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:36:31.939 --> 00:36:33.858  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you make even</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the slightest miscalculation,</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:34.025 --> 00:36:35.860  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
