<c.bg_transparent>and kill everyone.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:36.027 --> 00:36:37.695  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What other choice do I have?</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:36:37.862 --> 00:36:40.156  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I can get</c.bg_transparent><i><c.bg_transparent> Voyager</c.bg_transparent></i>
