641
00:37:42.593 --> 00:37:43.886  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:46.013 --> 00:37:47.348  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put down your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:37:48.516 --> 00:37:49.892  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
