<c.bg_transparent>Do you mind telling me why B'Elanna</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>burned out the deflector dish?</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:21.687 --> 00:41:23.272  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I ordered her to do it.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:41:24.023 --> 00:41:25.107  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Janeway]</c.bg_transparent>
