00:41:27.610 --> 00:41:29.028  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which was what, exactly?</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:41:29.570 --> 00:41:31.780  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
