697
00:41:38.245 --> 00:41:40.039  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you say we finish our dinner?</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:41:44.752 --> 00:41:47.922  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forget particle fountains</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and subspace inversions.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:41:48.088 --> 00:41:51.592  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There isn't an anomaly scarier</c.bg_transparent>
