701
00:41:54.637 --> 00:41:56.472  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember watching a bolt of lightning</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:41:56.639 --> 00:41:59.642  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
