703
00:41:59.808 --> 00:42:01.894  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd climbed it just a few hours before.</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:42:02.061 --> 00:42:03.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good timing.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:42:03.896 --> 00:42:06.524  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, what would have happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you hadn't turned our deflector dish</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:42:06.690 --> 00:42:08.275  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>into a lightning rod?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:42:09.193 --> 00:42:11.111  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've been down this road before.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:42:11.278 --> 00:42:12.655  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have we?</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:42:12.821 --> 00:42:15.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You wanting answers to questions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you shouldn't ask.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:42:16.951 --> 00:42:18.452  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But something did happen...</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:42:18.619 --> 00:42:22.081  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>outside the normal</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>space-time continuum.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:42:25.459 --> 00:42:26.710  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's strange...</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:42:27.711 --> 00:42:30.756  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>thinking there's a piece of your life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you don't know anything about.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:42:31.465 --> 00:42:33.092  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
